@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_qaumbl(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = 0.77
    v0 = wp.sin((0.07 - (v1 + 0.10 * v0 + 0.04)))
    v0 = tmp
    v1 = (wp.exp(v1) / v1)
    v1 = (v2 + ((v0 + 0.45 / v1 + 0.83) / 0.62))
    data[tid] = v0
